name: Sae Mask Boy
description:
The last Boy from kekarangan (Balinese architecture ornament) is finally here.
Say Hi to Sae Boy
Karang Sae is a Balinese ornamental sculpture, in philosophy it can be a Guardian an bring an positive energy in Balinese traditional building. Usually placed on every traditional door or dwelling in building, commonly you can view it in temple or in a palace.
